Barry Habib, chief strategy officer 
at RPM, founder of Mortgage Market Guide, and lead producer of 
the musical "Rock of Ages," discusses what it takes to be a 
'serial entrepreneur.'  Habib talks to Kathleen Hays on "The 
Hays Advantage" on Bloomberg Radio.  (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 19:08
 